<title>Banning face covering</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt; Denmark &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/world/2018/feb/06/danish-government-proposes-ban-on-full-face-veils&#34;&gt;is proposing&lt;/a&gt; to prohibit people from covering their faces in public. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; Unless the law also ban face recognition systems pointed at public places, in an effective way that can&amp;#39;t easily be bypassed, this would attack everyone&amp;#39;s rights. &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; If you live in Denmark, please talk with your legislators!   &lt;/p&gt;</content>
