<title>Ozone depletion</title>
<content type="html" xml:lang="en">&lt;p&gt; Ozone depletion in the stratosphere is getting worse, &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2018/feb/06/ozone-layer-not-recovering-over-populated-areas-scientists-warn&#34;&gt; in the latitudes where people mainly live. &lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt; This despite the fact that the depletion over Antarctica is gradually decreasing.    &lt;/p&gt;</content>
